    "John Trapp": "A rest to the people of God ] Gr. A sabbatism, an eternal rest, a sabbath that hath neither evening, #Ge 2:2 , nor labour, #Re 14:13 . But they shall enter into peace, rest in their beds, #Isa 57:2 ; be ravished in spirit, receive the full import and purport of the weekly sabbath, rest from travail and trouble, #Re 1:10 .\n9. A rest to the people of God] Gr. A sabbatism, an eternal [v_Gen_2_2] rest, a sabbath that hath neither evening, #Ge 2:2, nor labour, #Re [v_Isa_57_2] 14:"
